Webex App | Make someone a moderator of a space
In Webex App, if you're a moderator in a space, you can add others to the space, remove people, edit the space, and assign others as moderators. Keep in mind that even if you've created the space, you're not a moderator unless you chose to moderate the space from the space settings.
Desktop
iOS
Android
Web
Go to Messaging , select the space, and click People. Then click Add people, right-click the person's name, and select Assign as Moderator.

  If you want to remove someone as a moderator, right-click on the person's name and select Remove as Moderator.